cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.MM, cs.LG 

This paper deals with the task of near similar image search using features from Deep Neural Network to compare images and measure similarity. It also involves text data and explores the vast data to compute k-nearest neighbors using both image and text. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, since the paper deals with natural language processing and text matching, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is also a likely sub-category. The paper also involves multimodal data, which can fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
